issue_description: The brakes on my rental bike are not working properly, it's taking a lot of effort to slow down and stop. I'm having to squeeze the brake levers really hard to get any response, which is kinda scary. I'd appreciate it if someone could take a look and fix the issue ASAP.

The chain on my rental bike keeps slipping off the gears, making it hard to pedal. I've tried adjusting it, but it doesn't seem to be staying in place. I'd appreciate it if someone could take a look and fix the issue so I can continue my ride.
